fix: Electron black screen resolved

Root cause: Vite was building with absolute asset paths (/assets/...)
which resolve to filesystem root under file:// protocol in Electron.

Fixes:
- ui/vite.config.js: added base:'./' for relative paths in dist
- ui/index.html: added CSP meta tag for localhost connections
- desktop/main.js: added webSecurity:false to allow file:// -> http://localhost:4000
- START_ACC.bat: cleaned up launcher script

Result: Electron window now renders full React dashboard
